WEBVTT

00:04:57.625 --> 00:05:00.000
particularly in resource-limited settings.

00:05:02.292 --> 00:05:04.601
The first barrier is mutation:

00:05:04.625 --> 00:05:07.226
viruses mutate, our drugs don't.

00:05:07.250 --> 00:05:09.083
The second barrier: adherence.

00:05:10.042 --> 00:05:13.542
It's really hard to get these drugs
to those who need the most.

00:05:14.708 --> 00:05:19.583
I can't even adhere to a week-long
antibiotic regimen in this country.

00:05:22.292 --> 00:05:25.143
We're asking those
in resource-limited settings

00:05:25.167 --> 00:05:26.559
who face enormous adversity

00:05:26.583 --> 00:05:28.500
to adhere to lifelong regimens.

00:05:29.375 --> 00:05:32.768
And the third barrier is deployment,